{"tid":2509996,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國證券交易委員會：數字人民幣不會取代美元主導地位","createTime":"2021-04-30T00:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T01:04:15.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a333ae58429c372c09be87ced6f43da27f3cd74f","tid":2509996,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T00:28:16.000Z","msg":"美國證券交易委員會(SEC)一名高級官員表示，中國計劃推出的數字人民幣，不會取代美元的主導地位，由於穩定幣(Stablecoin)崛起，將維持美元地位，<strong>形容穩定幣本質是民間美元，所以美元仍將相當重要</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n穩定幣是由民間發行，通常由美元支持的加密貨幣，可以模擬美元等法定貨幣價值。<br />\n<br />\n包括人民銀行及聯儲局等全球主要央行，正加大力度自主研發數字貨幣，改善支付系統，應對來自加密貨幣的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>人行在有關方面的工作遠遠領先其他央行，數字人民幣亦有助推動人民幣國際化，並降低人民幣匯率。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588527-20210430.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588527-20210430.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwXjBGfL1Jh2LWroBhk3D7pk%3D&h=a2f66922\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588527-20210430.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=028c1660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588527-20210430.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ada7fedd69c4e74d08ca061f121166880d9e27ae","tid":2509996,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"即係聯儲局唔洗自己發行數字美元<br />\n<br />\nUSDT, TUSD, USDC 呢啲stablecoin已經將美元帶入加密貨幣世界<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7a292c757f09fac17fd344c975dbeb5ec3468a","tid":2509996,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T00:43:29.000Z","msg":"如果btc 係由人民幣計價咁威脅到lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fd49be040b4bad780c77